OL,6,FBibby Stockholm staff joked there was
OL,7,F"one less Muslim mouth to feed" after
OL,8,Fan asylum seeker on board died, a
OL,9,Fformer cleaner on the barge has
OL,10,Fclaimed.
OL,12,FThe incident is said to have happened
OL,13,Fshortly after Leonard Farruku, an
OL,14,FAlbanian asylum seeker, died while
OL,15,Fliving on board the barge in December.
OL,17,FThe 27-year-old is thought to have
OL,18,Ftaken his own life.
