OL,6,F'The Bibby Stockholm: A People's
OL,7,FInquiry' spoke to a number of former
OL,8,Fresidents for first-hand accounts of
OL,9,Fwhat life was like on the vessel.
OL,11,FThe report - produced by Care4Calais,
OL,12,FStand Up To Racism, and the Portland
OL,13,FGlobal Friendship Group - called for
OL,14,Fthe immediate closure of the barge and
OL,15,Fno renewal of its contract, as well as
OL,16,Finvestment in asylum claim decision-
OL,17,Fmakers.
