OL,6,FLevana, who worked as a cleaner on the
OL,7,Fbarge from its opening until late
OL,8,FDecember, spoke at a meeting in
OL,9,FParliament launching the report.
OL,11,FThe ex-employee, who did not wish to
OL,12,Fgive her surname, said she heard other
OL,13,Fstaff "talking about Leonard and
OL,14,Flaughing and joking 'Oh that is one
OL,15,Fless Muslim mouth to feed'".
OL,17,FShe said: "It was just disgusting.
OL,18,FThat was the overall vibe from a lot
OL,19,Fof the workers there.
