OL,6,F"And I was starting to think, why put
OL,7,Fthese people that have these views and
OL,8,Fprejudice in charge of looking after
OL,9,Fhundreds of men who have come here for
OL,10,Fsafe haven?"
OL,12,FAsked by the PA news agency if she had
OL,13,Fraised the incident, which happened
OL,14,F"within a week" of Mr Farruku's death,
OL,15,Fshe said she did not feel able to do
OL,16,Fso.
