OL,6,F"Maybe I should have spoken out, but
OL,7,Fthe position I was in at that time it
OL,8,Fwas quite difficult to speak to them
OL,9,Fabout anything and I know it was
OL,10,Fsomething they would have just
OL,11,Fdismissed," she said.
OL,13,FIn testimony for the report, she said
OL,14,Fshe was given a warning by a manager
OL,15,Fon December 12 last year after
OL,16,Fstanding with two of the barge's
OL,17,Fresidents on their break.
