OL,6,FShe saidL "I was told that I was being
OL,7,Fgiven a verbal warning because I
OL,8,Fshould not be friendly with the
OL,9,Fservice users in this way.
OL,11,F"After this I worked one more booked
OL,12,Fshift and then was offered no further
OL,13,Fwork, even though other staff were
OL,14,Fbeing offered shifts."
OL,16,FLevana said she had found the
OL,17,Fresidents to be respectful, helpful
OL,18,Fand polite, but senior staff had made
OL,19,Fcomments that were "often hostile, and
OL,20,Fpossibly racist".
