OL,6,FThe first initials of refugees who
OL,7,Fgave evidence for the report were used
OL,8,Finstead of their names, to protect
OL,9,Ftheir identity.
OL,11,FA, a queer refugee who moved from the
OL,12,Fbarge only after charities lodged
OL,13,Fsafeguarding concerns, said the
OL,14,Fconditions left them feeling paranoid
OL,15,Fand they "felt like I was going insane
OL,16,Fas soon as I got there".
OL,18,FA said there was no privacy anywhere
OL,19,Fon vessel, adding: "On the barge I
OL,20,Fsometimes just felt like a zoo animal."
