OL,6,FAnother former resident, S, told the
OL,7,Finquiry: "When leaving and entering we
OL,8,Fhave to be scanned, like airport
OL,9,Fsecurity. Many people don't go outside
OL,10,Fbecause of this.
OL,12,F"They stayed inside and tried to do
OL,13,Fsomething in the 'common rooms'. But
OL,14,Fthere is not enough space for people.
OL,16,F"One day I was standing in the
OL,17,Frestaurant and I said the food was not
OL,18,Fgood. The security staff said 'Keep
OL,19,Fyour mouth shut and sit down'."
