OL,6,FIn January, the Home Office shelved
OL,7,Fplans to procure more barges to hold
OL,8,Fasylum seekers.
OL,10,FThe Bibby Stockholm was accommodating
OL,11,Fjust under half the number of migrants
OL,12,Fthe Home Office expected would be the
OL,13,Fcase at the end of that month.
OL,15,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,16,Fdo not recognise the claims made in
OL,17,Fthis report.
