OL,6,F"The Bibby Stockholm is part of the
OL,7,Fgovernment's plan to reduce the use of
OL,8,Fexpensive hotels and bring forward
OL,9,Falternative accommodation options
OL,10,Fwhich are more cost effective,
OL,11,Fsustainable and manageable for the
OL,12,Ftaxpayer and local communities.
OL,14,F"There are rigorous safeguarding
OL,15,Fprocesses in place on the barge.
OL,16,FResidents have access to health and
OL,17,Fsocial care services, including mental
OL,18,Fhealth support.
